des:
This is Broward County Chat Bot Skill. Please ask a question related to Broward County and our chatbot will provide you an answer.
For example you can ask 
How do I file a complaint?
What happens after I file a complaint? 
What types of enforcement actions do we issue?
How do I search for an enforcement action?
